dct_title_s: Oak Leaf Trail Milwaukee County, Wisconsin 2004
dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents planned, proposed, and existing Oak Leaf Trail bike facilities for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2004. The dataset was originally published by the Wisconsin Bicycle Federation on October 15, 2004.[This feature dataset encompassses all data pertaining to the planned, proposed, and existing Oak Leaf Trail bike facilities in Milwaukee County, Wisconsin.]
